name: Texture 02
description: After my grandmother passed away, I traveled to Morocco. I went to a small city called Essaouira and feel in love with it. I felt very overwhelmed there and was still going through my art therapy process by taking photos of the walls. This wall I found very funny as it shows a graffiti of a mosk (or at least that's what I think it is) and my grandmother was Muslim so I thought I had to take a photo.
